title: ‘Succession’ Season 3 Episode 3 With Sarah Snook
description:
Sean and Joanna rejoin to talk about the third episode of ‘Succession’ Season 3. They discuss the major tactical errors by Kendal, Tom’s attempt at self-sacrifice, and much more. Later Joanna talks to actor Sarah Snook about Siobhan’s major moves in this episode.
Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Joanna Robinson
Guest: Sarah Snook
Producer: Steve Ahlman
